The story behind my Rome balcony photos 😂...Ughhh the struggle of solo traveling!!! So I’m at this gorgeous location, decided to wake up at 5am, I thought I’d be able to get some cool pics when nobody is around, sounds doable right? Wrong! 🙈
I wake up at 5, do my makeup,get dressed (and no I wasn’t wearing this booby dress lol), look out the window, nobody is outside. Sunrise, I go out with my gear, camera, tripod, lenses...the whole thing. Find this beautiful location, set my tripod...and guess what? People start gathering around me (mostly men), I don’t even know where they came from, and then this huge garbage truck stops and blocks my view.
So I take my stuff and I decide to go find a different location...but all these people started following me, apparently I was the daily attraction...the garbage truck appeared there again. So I gave up, took my stuff, went back to the hotel and took these pics on the hotel room balcony...🤷‍♀️ I don’t know how people do this...😭 I need an instagram husband ASAP! 🙈🙈🙈
Dress from @catwalk_connection
#travelphotography #travel #rome #thespanishsteps #spanishsteps#pinkperception
